         <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-zinc-900 leading-none tracking-tight">Can You Get Disability Benefits for ADHD?</h1>
         <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">Yes, it is possible to receive SSDI or SSI benefits for ADHD, but the bar is high. The Social Security Administration requires strong evidence that ADHD severely limits your ability to work. Here is what you need to know.</p>
